cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper is about building a sememe knowledge base for multiple languages, which is a task related to natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning models for automatic sememe prediction, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel task and explores important factors and difficulties, which are related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
